1. *Očigledno* je da će sutra biti sunčano. (It is obviously going to be sunny tomorrow.)
2. Njegov uspeh je *očigledan*. (His success is obvious.)
3. *Očigledno* je da se situacija u zemlji pogoršala. (It is obvious that the situation in the country has worsened.)
4. *Očiglednim* je da je on preopterećen poslom. (It is obvious that he is overworked.)
5. On je *očigledno* zaboravio šta je rekao. (He obviously forgot what he said.)